{"tid":823930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東鐵綫多個車站擠滿候車市民　有人形容入閘後進退失據","createTime":"2018-09-17T02:00:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T02:25:58.000Z","uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8e509ae641a075b1bd631af72be7fec6f861ce15","tid":823930,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T02:00:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1418442_1_L_20180917095009.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1418442_1_L_20180917095009.jpg&h=3c1d5579&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙田站等候入閘的人龍排至新城市廣場。（市民提供圖片）<br />\n<br />\n山竹吹襲過後，本港早上交通大受影響，幾近癱瘓。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵東鐵綫多個車站擠滿乘客，在大圍站，有市民形容入閘後進退失據，只能在人群中等候。<br />\n<br />\n沙田站等候入閘的人龍排至新城市廣場，粉嶺站關閉，大批市民在站內等候。<br />\n<br />\n九龍塘只剩一個月台運作，單線雙程行車，大批乘客在月台上等候列車。"},{"pid":"403033f282f57baf36e2906b4140282691fd1af0","tid":823930,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T02:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1418442_2_L_20180917095009.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1418442_2_L_20180917095009.jpg&h=09f0e32a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1418442_3_L_20180917095009.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1418442_3_L_20180917095009.jpg&h=ac7b7324&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在大圍站，有市民形容入閘後進退失據，只能在人群中等候。（市民提供圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1418442_4_L_20180917095009.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1418442_4_L_20180917095009.jpg&h=622b8f8c&s={SIZE}\" />九龍塘只剩一個月台運作，單線雙程行車，大批乘客在月台上等候列車。（市民提供圖片）"},{"pid":"40b3cfd5725cfb1f58005e515460f083dac341bd","tid":823930,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T02:01:33.000Z","msg":"